Three family members were kidnapped from their Northcliff home earlier this week, just a few hours later three bodies were discovered by security guards in a veld. JOHANNESBURG - The Naidoo family from Northcliff say they strongly believe that the burnt bodies found in Centurion are of their kidnapped relatives.Two adults and a teenager were kidnapped from their home Northcliff earlier this week - just a few hours later three bodies were discovered while security guards were extinguishing a veld fire. The family of the kidnapped victims say there's uncertainty as to exactly what happened and they're still waiting for a forensic report.A relative says they visited the scene on Wednesday. We are still waiting for the forensics to be completed ... the DNA tests. But we did go out there today, we have a strong view that it is them. (Edited by Zinhle Nkosi)